{
  "stem": "11472.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we used to think that the police was coming for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we would try to hide, you know, under leaves, under, oh god-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we hear a man comes running.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he says that in Borshchiv is a, a very big Aktion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in that Aktion, they took away my Uncle Leib, my cousin Chaim, and my entire Kavolik family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They discovered a very big bunker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was the first day or second day of, of Passover.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they shot them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the children, they threw in alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the graves were so high that the peasants said that the bodies were rising.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, people are walking around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're saying, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where do we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do we do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The forest is not safe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have no place where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My little sister, Sima, is four years old at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's walking around just like the grown-ups and mimicking, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We became like-- we children mimic the grown ups.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, we, we are so desperate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The men already are told not to come back, to watch out, that the people with the shields are not safe anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, they are starting to make-- Borshchiv is going to become Judenfrei.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they are, they are-- the, the Aktions are getting closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they're, they're cleansing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're making-- this is 1943.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My Uncle Nisel went to a forester.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This forester-- my Uncle Schloime also went with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This forester had-- was a watchman for-- this forest belonged to a Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This forester was hiding a Jewish-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] owned this forest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had promised him this forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
